 84	
 85	You do this by creating files under the folders `templates/article_pages`, `templates/category_pages` or `templates/section_pages`.
 86	Learn more [here](https://support.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001948367).
 87	
 88	## Stylesheet and JavaScript
 89	
 90	We use Rollup to compile the JS and CSS files that are used in the theme - `style.css` and `script.js`. Do not edit these directly as they'll be regenerated during release.
 91	
 92	To get started:
 93	
 94	```console
 95	$ yarn install
 96	$ yarn start
 97	```
 98	
 99	This will compile all the source code in `src` and `styles` and watch for changes. It will also start `preview`.
