Path: install-radix.md
 1	# Add Radix Navigation Menu
 2	
 3	Run this command to add Radix Navigation to your project:
 4	
 5	```bash
 6	npm install @radix-ui/react-navigation-menu
 7	# or
 8	yarn add @radix-ui/react-navigation-menu
 9	```
 10	
 11	## Benefits of Using Radix Navigation
 12	
 13	1. **Accessibility**: Built-in ARIA attributes, keyboard navigation, screen reader support
 14	2. **Smooth Animations**: Native support for enter/exit animations
 15	3. **Focus Management**: Automatic focus handling for keyboard users
 16	4. **Collision Detection**: Smart positioning to avoid viewport edges
 17	5. **Composable**: Easy to customize styling while keeping functionality
 18	6. **TypeScript Support**: Full TypeScript support out of the box
 19	
 20	## Current vs Radix Comparison
